    <td width=84%><font face=Verdana size=2>So it's 12am EST and there's 
    about 20 of us online doing various things when all of the sudden King 
    Tormax pops.  Naturally we're all sick of listening to Dreadwar and 
    Brodie talking about how to pick up cheap hookers, so we figured we'd give it a shot.  
    Wow, Tormax with 24 people will be fun!  Well, we grabbed a 
    few anon people and flushed out some of the noobs hiding in IRC and scraped together 
    a nice crew to go give Tormax a run for his money.  </font>
    <p><font face=Verdana size=2>With only 2 Warriors and 5 Clerics this was 
    going to be a tough fight for sure...</font></p>
