<p><b><font face=Verdana size=5>Vulek, Vulak, Trixare, Beatim... scam 
anyone?:</font></b></p>
<p><font face=Verdana size=2>I suggest that anyone who plays on Povar reads 
this.  Last week this scammer posted on our boards saying he had some 
Thurgadin Armor for MQ.  Naturally this thread attracted Praonat the Halfer 
Tink as it flaunted a Plate BP.  This guy demanded the money (45k) up front 
prior to the MQ which was understandable.  Brodie verified he had the plate 
BP by asking him to equip it and he was able to, good.. legit you'd think.</font></p>
<p><font face=Verdana size=2>Well, after receiving the 45k this fag /q'd 
(excuse me, went linkdead).  He came back shortly after and said that he 
was having ISP issues and went LD (/q'd) again.  The next day he logged on 
his alt, Beatim, and had the nerve to ask Brodie if anyone in Triton has a Fungi 
for trade.  When Brodie pointed out who he was he played dumb and called 
Brodie an asshole... then he mysteriously disappeared!  The next day he 
shows up again as Beatim and we start to talk to him.  He claims it's a 
'friend on his character' and he doesn't want to get into the middle of this.</font></p>
<p><font face=Verdana size=2>If you play on Povar make sure you avoid all 
trades with this guy, hell... avoid all groups with him too.  He is a 
lying, scamming, cheating little 15 y/o kid who can't live up to his deals.  
People like this make me sick, fuck off please!</font></p>
